    "The findings confirm our earlier work from before the release of ChatGPT, that a wide range of tools is used during the writing process (Zhao et al., 2023).",
    "Perhaps ChatGPT will displace other tools, but at the time the study was conducted it was reaching a community of users well-versed in using digital tools.",
    "It was finding a unique place in helping understand assignment questions, aligning answers to the question and structuring ideas, but was also used to perform tasks such as summarisation and proofreading that others performed with pre-existing tools.",
    "Our findings suggested that students with higher English proficiency levels tended to use AI tools less frequently.",
    "The study confirms previous research, that students are keen to use generative AI and see it as part of a general trend in technology development (Chan and Hu, 2023)."
